{
  "texts": [
    "(3) Construct the new state P k+1 from the N e lowest-energy eigenstates of H k, i.e.",
    "[P k+1] ab = 1≤i≤Ne ψ i,a ψ * i,b.",
    "(4) If converged (we discuss convergence criteria in Sec.",
    "3.2.4), terminate and return the final state P f = P k+1.",
    "Otherwise, proceed to the next iteration.However, this straightforward iterative procedure is known to sometimes oscillate between two or more states, and fail to converge."
  ]
}